{"tid":2128637,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】隔離病床爆煲 醫管局籲百輕微患者在家等通知","createTime":"2020-07-28T05:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T05:53:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7b3755ac68bcec7af5f836832ab683a4f54bd717","tid":2128637,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:48:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200728/S5XOBIZDKYURUHYO47UANB4CLQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200728%2FS5XOBIZDKYURUHYO47UANB4CLQ%2F&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBpWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=2fd76786\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200728%2FS5XOBIZDKYURUHYO47UANB4CLQ%2F&h=66e1a89d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200728/S5XOBIZDKYURUHYO47UANB4CLQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】隔離病床爆煲 醫管局籲百輕微患者在家等通知<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oGnV0oglgwk3vHNonTrI3gFuiCU=/640x349/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LOBOWTY4NUQXB3BXEF22NJH4IY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoGnV0oglgwk3vHNonTrI3gFuiCU%3D%2F640x349%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLOBOWTY4NUQXB3BXEF22NJH4IY.png&h=5f208c8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三波武漢肺炎疫情爆發，醫療系統瀕臨崩潰，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n張子峯表示今個月3個星期內，新增的確診個案，相等於之前數個月的總數，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n張子峯指未來醫院將大。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何栢良批港府未統計豁免檢疫人士<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【武漢肺炎●全球疫情】世衞：武肺輕易成為最嚴重衞生緊急事件<br />\n<br />\n對於有指政府豁免檢疫33類人士是第三波疫情爆發的導火線，港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良今日在一個電台節目批評，港府相關豁免配套做得不清不楚，又指沒想到政府未有統計豁免檢疫人士數目，若處理不當，跨境人士有機會將病毒帶回內地，這樣變相是「危害國家安全」；他認為政府要優先為最多人數的豁免檢疫類別做檢測，同時加強執法。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良續指，本港的檢疫安排太多不足，政府未有徵用整間酒店作隔離設施，設立社區隔離中心亦沒有實際作用，他建議徵用酒店作檢疫中心，並將現時的檢疫中心轉為處理有輕微病症的病人，紓緩醫療壓力。<br />\n<br />\n政府昨日（27日）宣佈再收緊限聚令，何栢良認為政府收緊防疫措施是無可奈何及必須做的事，相信可阻斷傳播鏈。對於應否押後立法會選舉，何栢良認為鄰近疫情較嚴重的國家都可舉行選舉，相信做好防疫措施，如期舉行選舉問題不大。<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n打國際線 《蘋果》英文版免費試睇 按此了解更多<br />\n英文版已登錄新版《蘋果》App按此下載/更新<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JOUpQA7FsFNodk8auzm_iJNg-JA=/640x397/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5R7TYOVFAMVBVQS7TKZGCW54ZM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJOUpQA7FsFNodk8auzm_iJNg-JA%3D%2F640x397%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5R7TYOVFAMVBVQS7TKZGCW54ZM.jpg&h=9b539a5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良批評，港府相關豁免配套做得不清不楚，又指沒想到政府未有統計豁免檢疫人士數目。"},{"pid":"21eadab3c920bc1701fe77e7263a76250aa93ff4","tid":2128637,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:50:06.000Z","msg":"見工要等通知<br />\n死都要等通知"},{"pid":"9457d59ac7f8681758641642895cc7a9f3a98c01","tid":2128637,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21eadab3c920bc1701fe77e7263a76250aa93ff4","tid":2128637,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:50:06.000Z","msg":"見工要等通知<br />\n死都要等通知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:52:25.000Z","msg":"死都要排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"762539cb90dd246f9292b009462a65e6e13f97cf","tid":2128637,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:52:54.000Z","msg":"確診左 未入院 咁樣勞保有冇5分4人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ea209e163adbd7f87d57d7df8a1eee4b4d72ca","tid":2128637,"uid":198841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:53:37.000Z","msg":"總之跟住美國做包無錯架啦"}]}